a:["$","section","cmqb6j0qx000vost2ldvrjn2k",{"className":"relative overflow-hidden py-20","children":[null,["$","div",null,{"className":"relative z-10 container mx-auto px-4","children":[["$","$L3",null,{"children":["$","div",null,{"className":"text-center mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent mb-3","children":"Loved by travellers"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white drop-shadow","children":"What Our Travellers Say"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mx-auto mt-5 h-px w-12 bg-accent/60"}]]}]}],["$","$L18",null,{"testimonials":[{"id":"cmqb9wafi00206wt28k4fwqim","name":"Anita Gurung","location":"Pokhara, Nepal","rating":4,"content":"Booked the Kerala Backwaters trip for my parents' anniversary. They absolutely loved the houseboat experience and the tea plantations in Munnar. Great value for money and the booking process was super smooth.","imageUrl":null},{"id":"cmqb9wab4001z6wt23s7stmaz","name":"Michael Chen","location":"Singapore","rating":5,"content":"The Everest Base Camp trek was the adventure of a lifetime. Standing at the base of the world's highest mountain is something I'll treasure forever. The Vraman team's attention to acclimatisation made all the difference.","imageUrl":null},{"id":"cmqb9wa6s001y6wt2nnq7cvgo","name":"Priya Thapa","location":"Kathmandu, Nepal","rating":4,"content":"Great experience with the Chitwan safari. Saw rhinos up close on the jeep safari and the Tharu dance was a lovely evening. The only minor issue was the long bus ride from Kathmandu, but the lodge more than made up for it.","imageUrl":null},{"id":"cmqb9wa2a001x6wt2oxjncdpx","name":"Emma & Tom Wilson","location":"Sydney, Australia","rating":5,"content":"We chose Vraman for our honeymoon in Thailand. Bangkok was electric and Phuket was paradise. The team even arranged a surprise candlelit dinner on the beach. Beyond our expectations!","imageUrl":null},{"id":"cmqb9w9xv001w6wt2n7f8vzk5","name":"Rajesh Sharma","location":"Delhi, India","rating":5,"content":"Booked the Golden Triangle tour for my family. The driver was punctual, the hotels were excellent, and our guide brought the history to life. The sunrise at the Taj Mahal was a moment I'll never forget. Highly recommend!","imageUrl":null},{"id":"cmqb9w9th001v6wt20ovvp4rt","name":"Sarah Johnson","location":"London, UK","rating":5,"content":"Our Annapurna Base Camp trek was absolutely life-changing! The guide was incredibly knowledgeable and the tea-house accommodation was much better than expected. Vraman Holidays planned every detail perfectly — we didn't have to worry about a thing.","imageUrl":null}]}]]}]]}]
